      <title>哥伦比亚领导人在马杜罗同意下会见委内瑞拉反对派候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/petro-meets-venezuela-opposition-candidate-with-maduro-s-consent</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗在对加拉加斯进行旋风式访问期间会见了委内瑞拉反对派总统候选人曼努埃尔·罗萨莱斯，他将自己定位为席卷邻国的政治危机的调解人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/petro-meets-venezuela-opposition-candidate-with-maduro-s-consent</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 21:57:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界外汇交易者受人民币和美元的影响一样大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/world-s-fx-traders-are-as-much-at-mercy-of-yuan-as-the-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些策略师表示，中国观察家呼吁北京放松对人民币的控制，但他们需要注意这可能引发连锁反应，从而动摇新兴市场和发达市场货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/world-s-fx-traders-are-as-much-at-mercy-of-yuan-as-the-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 21:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如何投资、致富和退休</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/how-to-invest-get-rich-and-retire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果你年轻并且想变得富有，你绝对可以做出让你积累真正财富的决定。关键是每年储蓄直到退休，并将这些储蓄投入能够击败通货膨胀的投资，例如股票市场。 Bloomberg Opinion 的 Nir ​​Kaissar 解释了如何做到这一点。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/how-to-invest-get-rich-and-retire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 21:26:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚重启与中国的关系时值得关注的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bhp-treasury-wine-the-stocks-to-watch-as-australia-resets-relations-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京和堪培拉之间关系的改善正在提振面临贸易限制的澳大利亚股市的前景，酿酒商和一些农业行业被视为主要受益者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/bhp-treasury-wine-the-stocks-to-watch-as-australia-resets-relations-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 21:19:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴林银行大举招聘以重建私人贷款业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/barings-kickstarts-hiring-to-rebuild-its-private-credit-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在经历了多年来最大规模的资产管理突击搜查之后，巴林银行制定了一项重建其直接贷款团队的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/barings-kickstarts-hiring-to-rebuild-its-private-credit-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 14:19:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于干预风险增加，美国数据公布后日元跌幅加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/yen-slides-past-152-per-dollar-boosting-intervention-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元暴跌至华尔街警告的水平，可能会促使日本当局进入市场以支持日元，然后继续下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/yen-slides-past-152-per-dollar-boosting-intervention-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:40:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员认为，随着收益率飙升，美联储将等到夏季之后才会降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/yields-soar-as-traders-price-in-just-two-fed-rate-cuts-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新一轮通胀加剧导致国债收益率飙升至 2024 年高点之后，投资者发出信号，美联储今年将从 9 月开始降息两次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/yields-soar-as-traders-price-in-just-two-fed-rate-cuts-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 12:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国考虑禁止向买家收取贷方产权保险费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/us-weighs-ban-on-charging-homebuyers-for-lender-title-insurance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国一家顶级消费者监管机构正在考虑是否禁止抵押贷款银行家向购房者收取保护贷方的产权保险费用，从而结束长期的行业惯例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/us-weighs-ban-on-charging-homebuyers-for-lender-title-insurance</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 10:30:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国通胀延迟导致新兴资产下滑 美联储降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/earnings-optimism-underpins-em-equity-gains-driven-by-ai-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国通胀数据高于预期，抑制了美联储将降息的预期，新兴市场货币下跌，股市涨幅也有所回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/earnings-optimism-underpins-em-equity-gains-driven-by-ai-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 09:43:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标准普尔 500 指数受到美联储转向重新思考和战争恐慌的打击：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在另一份热门通胀报告暗示美联储今年不会急于降息后，华尔街交易员导致股票和债券下跌。随着地缘政治紧张局势再度浮现，油价攀升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 22:14:02 GMT</pubDate>
